arts.ttl: Harrogate edge past Gainsborough to reach third round
arts.sum: Watch highlights as Harrogate Town book their place in the third round of the FA Cup as Dean Cornelius’s second-half header knocks out seventh-tier Gainsborough Trinity.

arts.ttl: Harrogate end Gainsborough’s run in FA Cup
arts.sum: Dean Cornelius headed the only goal.
